Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought an appraiser with me today, and I thought I'd ask him one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, please
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his is a fine Hina doll set
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A famous doll craftsman in\NKyoto seems to have made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much will you sell it to me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you buying these dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too late, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were already given to Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't have a daughter so\NI'm not interested in dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I want her to sell me is the hanging scroll behind all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Thunder God that was drawn by
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,an artist of the Edo era named Tetsuyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the Wind God which is the other half of this hanging scroll,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I really want to make it a complete set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, my husband says he has no intention of selling it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and besides, it doesn't\Nlook to be something so valuable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you know?\NHow valuable that hanging scroll is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much insurance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your husband's late father placed on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,20,000,000 yen, 20,000,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told your husband that I would pay him double that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I feel sorry for this hanging scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If kept in this manner, the value of this scroll will go down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be wiser to sell it to a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,professional collector like\NMr. Tsumagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will not sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much money you dish out for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be back again tonight just about the time your husband comes home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll agree to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I mention the story about him making a great loss in stocks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's put away the dolls and hurry on home too, then
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nostalgic, it's already been\N10 years since we last decorated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dolls look happy that they were
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,taken out of the box after such a long time too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi, would it be okay to decorate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,these dolls here until Girls' Day Festival this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess mother wants to say goodbye to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!\NBut, can I stay here a while longer then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I have one more picture I want to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have mother serve you some sweet sake then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought we were out of the ingredients to make it from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go out soon too
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy it then!\NThe supermarket is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi, isn't it about time you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you want to take a picture of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you want to take a picture of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you want to take a Ricture of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A picture of all of us having a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just took one like that a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just took one like that a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, just a little while more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was just around this corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the appraiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you went home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I forgot my cell phone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called my cell phone, then the lady
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,answered and told me that it's in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me I could get it when I go over tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I may get important phone calls so
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided toe pick it up now.\NBut, it seems that no one's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean grandma isn't home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's right, nobody's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,NO one is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the door's not locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if grandma went to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's the sound of the fax machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's coming from this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on!\NThe room is super messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fax seems-to be from her husband
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem to be the only place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Burglary. A burglar broke in after we left
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the looks of it, maybe the other rooms are messed up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad the dolls are fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room looks untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where grandma is, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that grandma's not the only one who disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hanging scroll of the\NThunder God is gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's call the police right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so I did miss you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, when I looked I found out that I had also run
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,out of sugar, so I went to buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:15:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, why are you all\Nlooking pale faced about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, the thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Setsuko, I thought you went out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot my wallet so\NI came back to get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bedroom's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so we were just about to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Iv.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Tsumagari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?\NI heard somebody scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A burglar, a burglar broke in .
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's talk after the police get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so from what a gather here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,those children came here to decorate the Hina dolls; and after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tsumagari who extremely-wanted the hanging scroll thatflwas stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,brought appraiser, Mr. Mie with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, please don't say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after the two men left, you five went out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, to buy the ingredients for making sweet sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ingredients for sweet sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother was going to make sweet sake for everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I realized that we were out of the necessary ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I had to go out,\NI asked the children to go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that you were here alone,\NGrandma Yayoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything then?\NLike strange noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was quiet, until the cell phone that he forgot in the living room rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you forgot your cell phone in the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were shown into the living room first,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because the children were in the Japanese room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we wanted to see the hanging scroll as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so forced our way immediately into the Japanese room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, after the phone call you seem to have gone out shopping too, but for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went out to buy sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I realized that we were out of sugar so I rushed out to get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know about what time it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was right after I hung up so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, can tell what time it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before I hung up. I heard the sound of the FAX on the other side of the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if we look at the time the FAX was sent, we can find out what time it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was the FAX from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was from my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then where is that original FAX?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My gosh, they really went all out messing up the room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the FAX you received from your husband
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3:218 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What else was stolen besides the hangingrscroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Only hererand the bedroom were ransacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the wallet that was on the shelf above the TV was left untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I have a minute with you, Officer Momose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the burglar broke in from the veranda facing this window,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that this is the way the burglar broke in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're on the 6th floor, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a common target for burglars who use a rope to get down from the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem to think that people living on the top floor of condos are rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and most times the windows aren't locked anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure know a lot, don't you Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, because ll live with an old man who likes to watch wide shows on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, you're the first ones
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who realized that the room was ransacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when we got back from shopping the front door was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when we heard the sound of the FAX machine and came into the living-room,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all messed up! At that time the clock on the FAX was 15:40!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the burglary took place between
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,15:30 and 15:40 a period of 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The burglar went down on the veranda and came in through thatswindow, rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were me,\NI'd be tooascared to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you close the window, nothing is in view from the veranda because of the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F the burglar opens the window wanting to look inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the curtain would flutter in the wind, and the lady on the phone would notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, besides the time thezEAX was sent out all show 15728!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the FAX kept coming
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in all-the while we were out shopping until we came back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think a burglar would break
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,into airoom where noise is constantly coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's just the sound of the FAX...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The more so frightening because it's the FAX!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because if the FAX completes coming in and the buzzer sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,somebody in the house may come to take a look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beside, it's strange that the burglar didn't notice her wallet and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if the burglar couldn't find what he was after,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wouldn't all the other rooms be ransacked too?
